      <minor />
      <comment>r2.7.1) (robot Adding: [[hi:मंदनाड़ी]]</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{SignSymptom infobox 
 | Name           = Bradycardia
 | Image        = Sinusbradylead2.JPG
 | Caption       = Sinus bradycardia seen in lead II with a heart rate of about 50.|
 | DiseasesDB     = 
 | ICD10          = {{ICD10|R|00|1|r|00}} 
 | ICD9           = {{ICD9|427.81}}, {{ICD9|659.7}}, {{ICD9|785.9}}, {{ICD9|779.81}} 
 | ICDO           = 
